00:41:26.390 --> 00:41:29.120
the story she was probably
most afraid to tell,

00:41:29.120 --> 00:41:36.700
because as she's now put
out, it's her family's story.

00:41:36.700 --> 00:41:41.900
And I think that's
what we all have to do.

00:41:41.900 --> 00:41:45.820
