00:43:21.070 --> 00:43:24.010
I don't know.

00:43:24.010 --> 00:43:25.790
I've never thought
about it that way.

00:43:25.790 --> 00:43:26.550
LAUREN LEADER CHIVEE: Yeah.

00:43:26.550 --> 00:43:27.966
And that is, I
think, in some ways

00:43:27.966 --> 00:43:32.230
a gray-- I don't know if
other people may disagree.

00:43:32.230 --> 00:43:35.480
There are gray areas on these
issues, but I do think, to me,

00:43:35.480 --> 00:43:38.310
there's no gray area,
no gray area whatsoever

00:43:38.310 --> 00:43:41.420
when we are hiring white actors
to play minority characters.

00:43:41.420 --> 00:43:42.920
It's just unacceptable.

00:43:42.920 --> 00:43:44.680
This happened in the
