00:43:44.680 --> 00:43:46.150
It happened in
the movie "Aloha."

00:43:46.150 --> 00:43:47.385
We continue to do this.

00:43:47.385 --> 00:43:48.780
It's absolutely unacceptable.

00:43:48.780 --> 00:43:52.880
